=== 0.9.X ===
* Deal with empty facet queries
* Passing an integer into the second argument of dynamic_facet() when multiple facets are requested gives the wrong value
* Automatically sort values passed into range queries
=== 0.10 ===
* Highlighting
  * Expose Highlights as strings from the Hit object
  * Ability to get _all_ highlights for a hit, or just the one for :a_field
  * Support all of Solrs highlighting configuration strings
  * Ability to format the highlights at display-time -- highlight.format{|word| "<strong>#{word}<strong>"}
* LocalSolr
* Text field restrictions
* Prefixes
* Intelligently decide whether to instantiate all facet rows at once
